Random
========================================================

```{r}


for (i in 1:10) {
  www = "http://www.random.org/integers/?num=10000&min=800000&max=2000000&col=1&base=10&format=plain&rnd=new"
  data = read.table(www)
  sub = data.frame(Id=0:9999 , Predicted=data$V1)
  
  fn = paste("/Users/gino/kaggle/fast-furious/gitHub/fast-furious/dataset/random-number-grand-challenge/",paste(paste("sub",i,sep=''),".csv",sep=''),sep='')
  
  write.csv(sub,quote=F,row.names=F,file=fn)
  
  }

```
